<item>
            <title>[LU-15420] Linux kernel 5.15 support</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15420</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Main changes needed to support Linux kernel 5.15 include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Compile the kernel with warnings as errors (WERROR) &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;N/y/?&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; (NEW)&lt;br/&gt;
(kernel commits 3fe617ccafd6f5bb33c2391d6f4eeb41c1fd0151 and b339ec9c229aaf399296a120d7be0e34fbc355ca)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Remove deprecated CPU-hotplug functions get_online_cpus() and put_online_cpus()&lt;br/&gt;
(kernel commit 8c854303ce0e38e5bbedd725ff39da7e235865d8)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Add rcu argument to -&amp;gt;get_acl() callback&lt;br/&gt;
(kernel commit 0cad6246621b5887d5b33fea84219d2a71f2f99a)&#160;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
